description:
Introducing the 2016 Honda Accord EX-L, a sleek and powerful sedan that will take your driving experience to the next level. With its 2.4L I4 engine, generating a impressive 185 horsepower and 181 foot-pounds of torque, you'll feel the thrill of the open road every time you get behind the wheel. And with the added convenience of a CVT transmission, you'll experience smooth and effortless shifting as you cruise down the highway.

But the 2016 Honda Accord EX-L is more than just a powerful and efficient machine, it also boasts a luxurious interior that will make every journey a comfortable one. The spacious cabin is designed with high-quality materials and features leather-trimmed seats, providing both style and comfort. And with the EX-L trim, you'll also enjoy added features such as a power moonroof and heated front seats.

Safety is always a top priority, and the 2016 Honda Accord EX-L has you covered with its advanced safety features. With the Honda Sensing suite, you'll have access to technologies such as lane departure warning, forward collision warning, and adaptive cruise control, giving you peace of mind on every drive.

Don't miss your chance to own this 2016 Honda Accord EX-L. With its sleek design, powerful performance, and luxurious features, it's the perfect combination of style and functionality. Come take a test drive and experience the excellence of the 2016 Honda Accord EX-L for yourself. We do service every vehicle in our inventory, and all vehicles come with a warranty .

Designed with the discerning driver in mind, the Lexus ES 350 delivers a level of luxury and sophistication that is truly unparalleled. Contact us today to learn more about this exceptional offering and how it can enhance your driving experience.

description:
Forget "stock." This is the Raptor Ford should have built. With only 30,000 miles, this 2019 Raptor has been professionally upgraded to deliver more power, better throttle response, and the aggressive sound a truck like this deserves.

The 2019 is the "sweet spot" for the Gen 2 Raptor, featuring the Fox Live Valve active suspension that adjusts in real-time to your terrain. This truck hasnt just been pampered, its been perfected.

Performance Upgrades:

Cobb Stage 2 Power Package: Includes the Cobb Accessport V3, high-flow air intake, and a larger front-mount intercooler. This setup safely bumps the horsepower and torque significantly over stock while improving cooling.

Corsa Performance Exhaust: Known for the best sound in the industry with zero cabin drone. It gives the EcoBoost a deep, menacing growl when youre on it, but stays refined at highway speeds.

Accessport Included: Allows you to monitor engine vitals in real-time and switch between performance, tow, or valet tunes instantly.
This truck is a head-turner that sounds as mean as it looks. Its never been jumped, thrashed, or smoked in. If you want a Raptor that stands out from the crowd and has the performance to back it up, this is it.

Priced so heavily discounted due to Rebuilt/Salvage title. For more information, please call dealer at (515) 265-1467. OTHER NOTABLE FEATURES AND OPTIONS YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT: Equipment Group 250A
    Safety and Security
    • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
    • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.

This 2020 Nissan Altima 2.5 SR, has a Pearl White Tricoat exterior and Charcoal interior color with only 20,415 miles. Stock Number DV13314. You can connect with us by calling 515-265-1467. OTHER NOTABLE FEATURES AND OPTIONS YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT: Premium Package ($1,090 value)
  • Heated Front Seats
  • Heated Outside Mirrors
  • Single Panel Moonroof
Safety and Security
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Rear collision mitigation - It has your back. Rear collision mitigation uses sensors to monitor the area behind you. If it senses an impending crash, it activates certain features to help prevent a collision or reduce the severity of it. Put your worries behind you with rear collision mitigation.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.

Discover the smarter way to buy your next vehicle at Vision Ford Lincoln, where car buying is fast, fair, and refreshingly simple. Our 15-Minute Car Deal means you can go from test-drive to signed deal in as little as fifteen minutes — no games, no pressure, just great cars and even better people. As your local Ford and Lincoln experts, were proud to deliver upfront pricing, transparent trade values, and a team thats focused on making your experience effortless from start to finish. Whether you shop online or in-store, Vision Ford Lincoln is where convenience meets confidence — because buying a car shouldnt take all day. Discover the perfect blend of style, efficiency, and advanced technology with this highly sought-after 2020 Ford Fusion SE. This stunning sedan, finished in Iconic Silver Metallic with a sleek Ebony interior, is turning heads and flying off our lot at Vision Ford Lincoln.

With only 8,700 miles on the odometer, this certified pre-owned Fusion is practically new and ready for its next adventure. The fuel-efficient 1.5L EcoBoost engine delivers impressive performance while keeping your fuel costs down, making it an ideal choice for both daily commutes and weekend getaways.

One of the most desirable features of this Fusion is the inclusion of both Apple CarPlay and Android Auto compatibility, allowing you to seamlessly integrate your smartphone with the vehicle's infotainment system. The SYNC 3 Communications & Entertainment System, with its 8-inch touchscreen display, provides intuitive control over your music, navigation, and more.

Safety is paramount in this Fusion, equipped with the Ford Co-Pilot360 Assist package. This comprehensive suite of driver-assist technologies includes Blind Spot Information System (BLIS), Lane-Keeping Assist, and Automatic Emergency Braking, giving you peace of mind on every journey.

The interior of this Fusion is designed for comfort and convenience. The 10-way power driver's seat with 2-way power lumbar support ensures you find your perfect driving position, while the dual-zone automatic climate control keeps you and your passengers comfortable in any weather.

Other standout features include:
- Push-button start with proximity key
- Auto-dimming rearview mirror
- Dual 12V DC power outlets
- FordPass Connect 4G mobile hotspot
- Wireless phone connectivity
- Cruise control with steering wheel controls
- Remote engine start via smart device

This Fusion also comes with the added benefit of being a certified pre-owned vehicle, giving you extra confidence in your purchase. With its low mileage, advanced features, and excellent condition, this 2020 Ford Fusion SE is an exceptional value that won't last long on our lot.

Don't miss your chance to own this in-demand sedan. Visit Vision Ford Lincoln today and experience the perfect combination of style, efficiency, and technology that this Fusion has to offer. With its popularity and limited availability, we recommend acting quickly to secure this outstanding vehicle before someone else does! description:
The 2020 Lincoln MKZ Reserve offers a refined blend of sophisticated luxury and confident capability, finished in a distinguished Blue exterior. Powered by a responsive 2.0L turbocharged I4 engine delivering 245 horsepower and 275 lb-ft of torque, this premium sedan provides smooth, poised performance for the daily drive through its seamless 6-speed automatic SelectShift transmission and an intelligent all-wheel-drive system for assured traction in all conditions.

The premium Reserve trim outfits the MKZ with distinctive 19-inch polished aluminum wheels, all-season touring tires, and a signature split-wing grille with LED lighting. Inside, you'll find premium leather seating surfaces, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, and elegant genuine wood interior trim. The driver-focused cabin offers a quiet, comfortable sanctuary, along with dual-zone automatic climate control and a 14-speaker Revel premium audio system for a first-class auditory experience.

Advanced technology features include the SYNC 3 infotainment system with an 8-inch touchscreen, Apple CarPlay and Android Auto compatibility, and a 4G LTE Wi-Fi hotspot. The MKZ Reserve also boasts Lincoln Drive Control with continuously controlled damping, a panoramic glass roof, and a comprehensive suite of Lincoln-exclusive driver-assist technologies for enhanced luxury, control, and confidence.

Crafted for serene comfort and elegant driving dynamics, this MKZ achieves an EPA-estimated 21 MPG city/31 MPG highway, making it a sophisticated and well-equipped choice for the discerning driver.

Experience Hassle-Free Shopping at Ames Ford Lincoln:

- Premium Quality Assurance: Rest assured with our meticulous vehicle inspections and reconditioning, averaging over $2,000 per car, ensuring your peace of mind when purchasing a pre-owned vehicle. That's why they're all backed by our 7-Day Like it or Return it Money Back Guarantee.

- Non-commissioned Sales Consultants: Means no pushy sales tactics, just friendly professionals to help you find the best car for your needs.

- Unmatched Transparency: Prior to your purchase, gain full visibility into the service history of the vehicle, ensuring complete transparency and confidence in your decision.

- Our Best Price Upfront: We recognize the extensive research done by shoppers, hence we offer highly competitive prices online to match your needs and expectations.

- Express Checkout for Time Efficiency: Streamline your purchase process by completing most of the deal remotely, whether from the comfort of your workplace or home, saving you valuable time.

Elevate your daily drive with this Quartz White 2020 Hyundai Sonata Limited FWD, a sophisticated midsize sedan that blends premium comfort, advanced technology, and impressive efficiency with 27/36 City/Highway MPG. Designed with the Limited Package and Option Group 01, this Sonata features luxurious leather seating surfaces with heated and ventilated front seats, a heated steering wheel, memory drivers seat, power moonroof, and striking 18-inch machine/argent finish alloy wheels. Stay confidently connected through the intuitive touchscreen display with built-in Navigation, Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, Bluetooth hands-free capability, SiriusXM, and a 12-speaker Bose Premium Audio system, plus the convenience of wireless phone charging and the Blue Link Connected Care & Remote Package with a 3-year subscription. Inside, enjoy dual-zone automatic climate control, a heads-up display, rain-sensing wipers, HomeLink garage door transmitter, and refined interior details that make every commute feel first class. This 2020 Hyundai Sonata Limited FWD delivers upscale style, innovative tech, and trusted Hyundai reliability in one exceptionally well-equipped sedan.

If you're looking for the perfect balance of tech, comfort, and low mileage value, this 2020 Ford Fusion S is calling your name. With under 20,000 miles on the odometer, this sleek sedan is practically fresh off the showroom floor and packed with next-gen features designed to keep your drive fun, safe, and connected.
Step inside and feel the modern sophistication of a thoughtfully designed cabin featuring front bucket seats, push-button start, and a multi-function display that keeps all your important info in view. Apple CarPlay, Bluetooth connectivity, voice-activated commands, and USB audio input make it a breeze to stream, navigate, and stay in control, while integrated apps and a connected car system give your tech-loving side something to celebrate.
Safety isn’t just a feature—it’s a lifestyle with the Fusion S. Equipped with accident avoidance systems, blind spot warning, rear cross traffic alert, and crash sensors, this car has your back from every angle. Stability control, electronic braking, and emergency braking prep deliver confidence in every mile, while curtain and side airbags provide added protection. The rearview camera and halogen headlights make parking and nighttime driving a breeze.
From its stainless steel exhaust tip and approach lights to the smooth feel of its FWD drivetrain, this Fusion delivers clean lines and crisp performance. With keyless entry, satellite radio, Wi-Fi compatibility, and that unmistakable Ford confidence, this Fusion S is the low-mileage, high-tech ride you’ve been waiting for.

HYUNDAI GET A WAY! YEAR END SAVING!

This 2020 Honda Clarity Plug-In Hybrid Touring is a remarkable opportunity for the discerning driver. With its sleek exterior, advanced hybrid powertrain, and an abundance of premium features, this vehicle is poised to exceed your expectations.

• Navigation System
• Four wheel independent suspension
• 4-Wheel Disc Brakes
• ABS brakes
• Heated Front Bucket Seats
• Perforated Leather-Trimmed Seats
• Wheels: 18" Hybrid Aerodynamic Alloy

Imagine effortlessly gliding through the city streets, enjoying the convenience of a plug-in hybrid system that delivers exceptional fuel efficiency without compromising performance. The Clarity's advanced powertrain seamlessly blends electric and gasoline power, providing a smooth and responsive driving experience that will leave you impressed.

Beyond the impressive powertrain, this Clarity Touring is equipped with a wealth of premium features that elevate your driving experience. The navigation system ensures you'll never get lost, while the four-wheel independent suspension and ABS brakes provide a confident and secure ride. The heated front bucket seats and perforated leather-trimmed upholstery offer unparalleled comfort, and the 18-inch hybrid aerodynamic alloy wheels lend a stylish touch to the exterior.

Stepping inside, you'll be greeted by a well-appointed cabin that caters to your every need. Enjoy the convenience of dual-zone automatic climate control, a premium audio system, and the seamless integration of Apple CarPlay and Android Auto. The power driver's seat and leather-wrapped steering wheel add a touch of luxury, while the rear-view camera and advanced safety features provide added peace of mind.

This 2020 Honda Clarity Plug-In Hybrid Touring is a true testament to Honda's commitment to innovation and craftsmanship. With its exceptional fuel efficiency, premium features, and striking design, it's an opportunity that simply cannot be missed. We invite you to experience the Clarity for yourself and discover the joy of driving this remarkable vehicle.

At our dealership, we are dedicated to providing our customers with the highest level of service and satisfaction. Our knowledgeable sales team is ready to answer any questions you may have and guide you through the purchasing process. We are confident that this Clarity Touring will exceed your expectations and become the perfect addition to your lifestyle.

We look forward to the opportunity to earn your business and help you find the vehicle of your dreams. Visit us today and let us demonstrate why the 2020 Honda Clarity Plug-In Hybrid Touring is the perfect choice for the discerning driver.

This 2020 Toyota Corolla Hybrid LE is an exceptional value, priced at just $20,703. With its sleek exterior design, advanced technology features, and impressive fuel efficiency, this Elantra is the perfect choice for the discerning driver seeking a versatile and reliable daily commuter.

Key features of this Elantra Value Edition include:

• Bluetooth
• Heated seats
• Blind Spot Monitors
• Rear view camera
• Power Windows & Locks
• Cargo Package (C1) with Reversible Cargo Tray, Cargo Net, and Trunk Hooks
• Carpeted Floor Mats
• Center Console Tray
• First Aid Kit

Under the hood, the Elantra Value Edition is powered by a 2.0L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine paired with a CVT transmission, delivering an impressive 30 city/40 highway MPG. This efficient powertrain provides a smooth and responsive driving experience, making your daily commute a pleasure.

The interior of the Elantra Value Edition is designed with your comfort and convenience in mind. Enjoy the premium cloth seat trim, heated front bucket seats, and a host of advanced technology features, including a Display Audio system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration. The spacious cabin and generous cargo capacity make this Elantra the perfect companion for your active lifestyle.

Safety is also a top priority in the Elantra Value Edition, with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features, including dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, electronic stability control, and a rearview camera. You can drive with confidence, knowing that you and your passengers are well-protected.

This 2020 Hyundai Elantra Value Edition is an exceptional value proposition, offering a impressive array of features and capabilities at a highly competitive price point. With its sleek design, advanced technology, and impressive fuel efficiency, this Elantra is the perfect choice for the discerning driver seeking a versatile and reliable daily companion.

We invite you to experience the 2020 Hyundai Elantra Value Edition for yourself. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional sedan can enhance your driving experience. We're confident that once you've had the opportunity to explore its features and capabilities, you'll be convinced that the Elantra Value Edition is the perfect choice for your next vehicle.

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this stunning 2020 Chevrolet Malibu Premier. Boasting a sleek silver exterior and a meticulously inspected and reconditioned interior, this Malibu Premier is ready to take you on the road in style and comfort.

• Completely inspected and reconditioned
• Service records available
• Navigation system
• Bose premium 9-speaker audio system
• Dual-zone automatic climate control
• Power driver's seat with memory
• Heated and ventilated front seats
• Heated rear seats
• Power moonroof
• Rearview camera

Powered by a robust 2.0L turbocharged 4-cylinder engine and paired with a smooth-shifting 9-speed automatic transmission, this Malibu Premier delivers an exceptional blend of performance and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 22 MPG in the city and 32 MPG on the highway. The Malibu's sophisticated suspension and precise steering provide a refined and engaging driving experience, while advanced safety features like forward collision alert, lane keep assist, and automatic emergency braking help keep you and your loved ones secure.

Inside, the Malibu Premier's cabin is a sanctuary of comfort and technology. The Bose premium audio system fills the cabin with rich, immersive sound, while the Chevrolet Infotainment 3 Plus system with built-in navigation keeps you connected and informed. Dual-zone automatic climate control ensures everyone rides in perfect comfort, and the heated and ventilated front seats, along with the heated rear seats, provide a level of luxury you'll appreciate on every journey.

This Malibu Premier is more than just a car – it's a statement of refined style and sophisticated technology. With its impressive list of features and the peace of mind that comes with a thoroughly inspected and reconditioned vehicle, this Malibu Premier is an exceptional value that deserves your attention. Schedule a test drive today and experience the difference for yourself.

Since 1972 Wiesner has been a name people around Houston and Conroe have trusted for great sales and service. Past Chairman of the Board and CEO John Wiesner was born in Richmond, Texas and grew up in Hempstead. He married Beth Sorsby, also of Hempstead. They were graduates of Southern Methodist University. Mr. Wiesner started his automotive career in Hempstead in 1949, then moved to Baytown. In 1977, he purchased the Buick-Pontiac-GMC dealership in Conroe which is now the main headquarters for the Wiesner Automotive Group. Today the Wiesner Family carries on the tradition started by their father and grand-father by maintaining that great level of trust through community involvement, promoting quality brands and standing behind the motto "Buy for Less at Wiesner".

description: Introducing the 2020 Toyota Camry LE, a striking blend of elegance, efficiency, and performance that promises to elevate your driving experience to new heights. This pristine white sedan is not just a car, it's a statement of style and sophistication, designed to turn heads wherever you go. With its sleek lines and contemporary design, the Camry LE embodies the perfect balance between modern aesthetics and timeless appeal. Under the hood, the Camry LE boasts a robust 2.5L I4 engine that delivers an impressive 203 horsepower and 184 ft-lbs of torque. This powertrain ensures a spirited drive, whether you're navigating city streets or cruising down the highway. Paired with an 8-Speed Automatic Transmission featuring Sequential Shift Mode, this vehicle offers seamless gear transitions, enhancing both performance and fuel efficiency. Experience the thrill of smooth acceleration and responsive handling, making every journey an exhilarating adventure. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by a spacious and inviting interior, adorned with plush gray cloth seating that exudes comfort and sophistication. The meticulously designed cabin offers ample space for both driver and passengers, ensuring a comfortable ride even on the longest trips. The intuitive layout of the controls and dashboard allows for easy access to all essential functions, putting everything you need right at your fingertips. The 2020 Toyota Camry LE is not just about looks and performance, it's also packed with features that prioritize your safety and convenience. With advanced safety systems at your disposal, you can drive with confidence knowing that Toyota's commitment to safety is always working to protect you and your loved ones. The Camry LE's reputation for reliability and durability means you can trust it to be a dependable companion for years to come. Beyond its impressive performance and safety features, the Camry LE offers a driving experience that is both engaging and economical. Its fuel-efficient design ensures that you can spend more time enjoying the open road and less time at the pump, making it an ideal choice for those who value both excitement and practicality. The exterior's white finish not only enhances the vehicle's sleek and modern look but also reflects a sense of purity and elegance, making it a versatile choice for any lifestyle. Whether you're heading to a business meeting or a weekend getaway, the Camry LE's refined appearance will always leave a lasting impression. In summary, the 2020 Toyota Camry LE is a remarkable vehicle that combines style, performance, and practicality in one stunning package. Its powerful engine, smooth transmission, and comfortable interior make it a joy to drive, while its advanced safety features and legendary reliability provide peace of mind. This is more than just a car, it's an invitation to experience driving in a whole new way. Don't miss the opportunity to own this exceptional vehicle. Visit us today and take the 2020 Toyota Camry LE for a test drive. Feel the excitement, experience the comfort, and discover why the Camry LE continues to be a favorite among drivers who demand the best. Your perfect drive awaits!

With an original MSRP of $21,485, this 2022 Nissan Sentra S delivers efficient performance and everyday practicality in a well-designed compact sedan. The four-speaker sound system offers clear, balanced audio for entertainment on the road, while intuitive controls keep everything within easy reach.

Safety and driver assistance features add confidence behind the wheel, highlighted by a rearview camera that assists with parking and low-speed maneuvering. Combining fuel efficiency, user-friendly technology, and a comfortable interior, this 2022 Nissan Sentra S is a smart and reliable choice for drivers seeking value, practicality, and modern features in a compact sedan.

description: The 2022 Kia Forte LXS is a compact vehicle that combines style, performance, and advanced safety features. This model is built with a robust 2L I-4 DOHC engine that delivers a commendable 147HP, paired with a smooth 2-speed CVT for effortless driving. Safety is paramount in the 2022 Kia Forte LXS, featuring cutting-edge technologies that enhance your driving experience. One of its standout features is **hands-on cruise control**, which allows you to set your speed and maintain a safe distance from other vehicles, transforming your road trips into relaxing journeys. This system ensures that your hands are always on the wheel, adding a layer of safety. Another impressive safety feature is the **forward collision mitigation** system. This technology actively monitors your surroundings and can prepare the vehicle for an impending collision, helping to reduce the severity of an accident. Its a proactive approach to driving safety that every driver will appreciate. The **rear camera** is another essential feature that aids in visibility. It provides enhanced images of the area behind you, ensuring that you can safely navigate tight spaces and avoid obstacles while reversing. To further enhance your driving safety, the Forte LXS is equipped with **lane departure prevention**. This feature detects unintentional lane drift and takes corrective action, ensuring you stay safely in your lane. Coupled with **brake assist**, which boosts your stopping power during emergency braking, the 2022 Kia Forte LXS is designed to keep you safe on the road. For those long drives, the **cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls** offers convenience by allowing you to maintain your speed without constant foot pressure. The **touchscreen** interface adds a modern touch, enabling easy access to various features at your fingertips. Performance-wise, the **variable valve timing** ensures that the engine operates efficiently across a range of RPMs, optimizing fuel efficiency and performance. The inline 4-cylinder engine offers a balance of power and economy, making it a smart choice for daily commuting. Finally, the **driver attention monitor** keeps an eye on your focus levels, alerting you if it detects drowsiness or distraction. This thoughtful feature underscores Kias commitment to safety and driver well-being. In summary, the 2022 Kia Forte LXS is an impressive vehicle packed with features that prioritize safety, convenience, and performance. If youre in the market for a reliable and stylish compact car, the Forte LXS is definitely worth considering!

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, technology, and efficiency in this 2022 Toyota Corolla SE. With its sleek silver exterior and a host of advanced features, this Corolla is poised to elevate your driving experience.

Elevate your commute with standout amenities, including:
• 6 Speakers
• SiriusXM Radio
• Automatic Climate Control
• Keyless Entry
• Steering Wheel Audio Controls
• Rear-View Camera
• Blind Spot Monitoring
• Lane Departure Warning
• Pre-Collision System with Pedestrian Detection

This Corolla SE also boasts exceptional fuel efficiency, delivering an impressive 31 city/40 highway MPG, ensuring you can go further on every tank. Slip behind the wheel and experience the smooth, responsive performance of the 2.0L I4 engine paired with a continuously variable transmission.

Beyond its practical benefits, the Corolla SE exudes a refined, sporty aesthetic. The sleek exterior lines, 18-inch alloy wheels, and integrated rear spoiler create a bold, head-turning presence. Step inside the well-appointed cabin and enjoy the premium fabric seating, leather-wrapped steering wheel, and thoughtful storage solutions.

Safety is paramount, and this Corolla SE delivers with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies. From the Blind Spot Monitor to the Pre-Collision System with Pedestrian Detection, you can drive with confidence, knowing you and your passengers are well-protected.

Whether commuting, running errands, or embarking on a weekend getaway, this 2022 Toyota Corolla SE is the perfect companion. Experience the perfect blend of style, technology, and efficiency that this exceptional vehicle has to offer. Visit our showroom today to take it for a test drive and discover why the Corolla SE should be your next automotive choice.

The 2022 Honda Accord Sport is lauded for its blend of sharp, athletic styling and practical daily usability, featuring a spacious, upscale cabin with significant legroom. Key strengths include powerful engine options (1.5L or 2.0L turbo), standard Apple CarPlay/Android Auto, and top-tier safety ratings. Key Advantages of the 2022 Honda Accord Sport Performance & Handling: The 2.0T variant offers a powerful 252-hp engine paired with a 10-speed automatic transmission, while the 1.5L offers efficient, capable performance. Sporty handling is a hallmark of this model. Interior & Comfort: Known for having a "cavernous" cabin, the Sport offers comfortable, leather-trimmed seats and a user-friendly infotainment system. Standard Features: The Sport trim includes 19-inch alloy wheels, a rear spoiler, fog lights, a 12-way power-adjustable driver's seat, and a leather-wrapped steering wheel. Technology & Safety: Comes standard with Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, and Honda Sensing safety features. The 2.0T specifically adds wireless connectivity. Practicality: Features a large trunk (17 cu. ft.) with 60/40 split-folding rear seats for added cargo versatility. Specific Trim Considerations Sport 2.0T: Often preferred for its increased power, 10-speed automatic, and, in some cases, added features like a sunroof. Sport 1.5L: Highly efficient for a daily driver. Sport SE: Adds heated seats and proximity keyless entry. Outstanding fuel economy and sleek styling are two great reasons to consider this Honda Accord Sedan. Low, low mileage coupled with an exacting maintenance program make this vehicle a rare find. The **2022 Honda Accord Sport** is a remarkable vehicle that is now more affordable with a recent price drop of $400. This is your chance to seize a fantastic deal on a car that masterfully combines performance, safety, and advanced technology. Don’t wait too long, as this price reduction makes it a great opportunity to elevate your driving experience.

Under the hood, the Accord Sport is equipped with a powerful 1.5L I-4 gasoline engine that delivers an impressive 192HP, coupled with a smooth continuously variable transmission CVT. This dynamic duo not only provides a thrilling driving experience but also remarkable fuel efficiency, making it perfect for both daily commutes and long road trips.

Safety is a top priority in the Accord Sport, featuring cutting-edge systems like **Lane departure prevention** and **Forward collision mitigation**. The lane departure prevention system actively monitors your lane position and takes corrective actions, ensuring you stay on track. Meanwhile, the forward collision mitigation system is always on alert, preparing for potential impacts and providing peace of mind while driving. Additionally, the **Front pedestrian impact prevention** technology enhances your awareness by detecting pedestrians in your path.

One of the standout features of the 2022 Honda Accord Sport is its **Adaptive cruise control with traffic stop-go**. This innovative system allows you to set your desired speed while maintaining a safe distance from the vehicle ahead, even coming to a complete stop if traffic requires it. This feature significantly reduces driver fatigue, making it an ideal companion for long journeys.

For those who appreciate convenience, the **Smart device mirroring** feature integrates your smartphone seamlessly with the vehicles infotainment system, allowing easy access to apps while keeping your focus on the road. The **Rear camera** enhances visibility when reversing, providing clear views of obstacles behind you, while **Brake assist** maximizes your stopping power in emergencies.

Comfort is also a priority in the Accord Sport, with features like **Power 4-way driver lumbar support** and a **Power reclining driver seat** that allow you to personalize your driving experience. These adjustments ensure every journey is not only safe but also comfortable.

In summary, the 2022 Honda Accord Sport is a stellar choice that excels in performance, technology, and safety features. With the recent price drop, this is an opportunity you wont want to miss. description: The 2022 Tesla Model 3 Long Range is a stylish, all-electric sedan that blends advanced technology with impressive performance. As a used vehicle in excellent condition, this Model 3 delivers an eco-friendly driving experience without sacrificing power or comfort. It boasts 346 horsepower and 389 lb-ft of torque, providing smooth acceleration with its AWD drivetrain. With an efficiency of 134 MPGe in the city and 126 MPGe on the highway, it’s ideal for daily commuting and long trips alike. Its modern design features a spacious four-door layout with seating for five, complemented by premium amenities like heated seats, a sunroof, and wireless charging, ensuring a luxurious ride. Advanced driver-assistance features such as adaptive cruise control, blind spot monitor, lane keep assist, collision warning, and a backup camera make every journey safer and more convenient. This Tesla Model 3 excels in connectivity and convenience, featuring a 15-inch infotainment touchscreen that controls navigation, entertainment, and vehicle settings. Bluetooth streaming, HD radio, and a 560-watt sound system with 14 speakers create an immersive audio experience. Tesla’s app allows remote control and vehicle management, with your phone serving as a key for easy entry. Additional features include rear heated seats, memory seats, and a comprehensive camera system recording front, rear, and side views for added security. Wi-Fi hotspot capability keeps passengers connected, making this vehicle perfect for tech-savvy drivers seeking performance, safety, and modern amenities. 2022 Tesla Model 3 Safety and Security Features The Model 3 prioritizes safety with advanced systems like traffic sign recognition that features adaptive speed limiting. Dual front knee airbags provide extra protection in collisions, while the front camera system enhances visibility. Parking sensors at the front and rear assist with precise maneuvering, supported by a regenerative braking system that boosts efficiency and safety. The dash camera system records footage from all angles, offering security and peace of mind. Four-wheel ABS ensures reliable stopping power in diverse conditions, making this Model 3 a trustworthy choice for everyday safety. 2022 Tesla Model 3 Entertainment and Technology Features Built for entertainment and connectivity, the Tesla Model 3 features a large 15-inch infotainment screen serving as the central hub. The Tesla app enables your phone to act as a key, providing seamless access and control. With 14 high-quality speakers powered by 560 watts, the sound system delivers clear, immersive audio. The app also allows remote climate control, charging management, and vehicle tracking for added convenience. Wi-Fi hotspot capability keeps passengers connected, and hands-free voice controls for calls and radio simplify operation. The intuitive touch screen makes every drive enjoyable and connected, combining modern technology with ease of use. 2022 Tesla Model 3 Performance Features The Model 3 Long Range offers an electric range of approximately 334 miles per charge, thanks to its lithium-ion battery. Charging takes about 10 hours with a 240V outlet, making recharging straightforward at home. Its full-time AWD system ensures excellent traction and handling in various conditions, providing a smooth yet dynamic ride. With quick acceleration and responsive handling, this Model 3 combines impressive power with efficiency. Its range, drivetrain, and performance features make it an ideal choice for drivers seeking a high-performance electric vehicle with modern safety and tech features.

description:
Discover the exceptional 2022 Hyundai Elantra SEL, a sedan that redefines the driving experience. With its sleek black exterior and impressive performance, this Elantra is the perfect blend of style and substance.

Boasting a comprehensive Convenience + Premium Package, the Elantra SEL offers a host of advanced features to elevate your commute:

• Wireless Device Charging
• Smart Cruise Control with Stop & Go
• Full 10.25" LCD TFT Cluster
• Heated Front Seats
• Bose Premium Audio System
• Power Sunroof

Complementing these premium amenities, the Elantra SEL also includes the Cargo Package, providing a reversible cargo tray, cargo net, and cargo block for seamless organization.

Under the hood, this Elantra is powered by a 2.0L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine, delivering an exceptional fuel economy of 31 MPG in the city and 41 MPG on the highway. With its front-wheel-drive configuration and continuously variable transmission (CVT), the Elantra SEL offers a smooth and efficient driving experience, whether navigating city streets or cruising down the highway.

The Elantra's striking black exterior is complemented by a host of premium design elements, including LED and bulb tail lights, chrome beltline molding, and dark chrome exterior accents. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed interior, featuring cloth seat trim, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, and a 60/40 split-folding rear seat with an armrest and cupholder.

Safety is paramount in the Elantra SEL, with features like Forward Collision Avoidance Assist, pedestrian and cyclist detection, and an emergency communication system through Hyundai's Blue Link Connected Car Service. The Elantra also boasts a suite of advanced driver assistance technologies, including ABS brakes, electronic stability control, and a rearview camera, ensuring a confident and secure driving experience.

This 2022 Hyundai Elantra SEL is a true standout in its class, offering a compelling blend of style, technology, and performance. Experience the difference for yourself – schedule a test drive today and discover the exceptional value this Elantra has to offer.

With the odometer reading an impressive 11,588 miles below market average, this Model 3 Performance represents a rare opportunity to own a meticulously cared-for example of Teslas high-performance sports sedan. Featuring dual-motor all-wheel drive and instant electric torque, it delivers blistering acceleration, razor-sharp handling, and confident traction in all conditions redefining what a performance vehicle can be.

Step inside the minimalist yet sophisticated cabin, where advanced technology and premium comfort take center stage. Premium heated front bucket seats with premium seat trim and memory settings provide exceptional comfort and personalization, while dual-zone automatic climate control with HVAC memory ensures an ideal cabin environment every time you drive. The intuitive layout places everything within easy reach, complemented by a high-end premium audio system that delivers rich, immersive sound for every journey.

At the heart of the experience is Teslas advanced infotainment system with built-in navigation, seamlessly integrated into the expansive central touchscreen. Driver-assistance features such as Active Cruise Control, Lane Departure Warning, Brake Assist, and ParkAssist front and rear enhance confidence and safety whether commuting or traveling long distances. Rain-sensing wipers, speed control, and steering wheel-mounted functions further elevate daily convenience.

On the exterior, the Model 3 Performance makes a bold statement with its sleek, aerodynamic profile and aggressive stance. The striking Deep Blue Metallic paint is perfectly complemented by the iconic 20 x 8.5 Uberturbine wheels, underscoring the vehicles performance-focused character. Fully automatic headlights ensure excellent visibility, while the split-folding rear seat adds practicality and versatility without sacrificing style.

This 2022 Tesla Model 3 Performance blends exhilarating acceleration, advanced technology, and everyday usability into one compelling package. description: The 2022 Honda Civic Sport is a remarkable vehicle that combines style, performance, and advanced technology. Equipped with a robust 2L I-4 gasoline direct injection engine, it delivers a dynamic 158HP and features a continuously variable transmission CVT for a smooth driving experience. One of the standout features of the Civic Sport is its *Smart device mirroring*, which seamlessly integrates your smartphone with the vehicles infotainment system. This feature enhances safety by allowing you to access your favorite apps while keeping your attention on the road, minimizing distractions. Safety is a top priority in the Civic Sport, highlighted by its *Forward collision mitigation* system. This state-of-the-art technology continuously monitors the road for potential collisions, preparing the vehicle to reduce the impact of an impending crash. Additionally, the *Front pedestrian impact prevention* feature actively scans for pedestrians, ensuring added protection in busy urban settings. For those who frequently encounter heavy traffic, the *Adaptive cruise control with traffic stop-go* system is invaluable. It automatically adjusts your speed to maintain a safe distance from the vehicle ahead, stopping the car if traffic halts and resuming speed effortlessly when the road clears. This feature significantly reduces the stress associated with daily commutes and longer journeys. The *Lane departure prevention* system and *Hands-on steering assist/lane centering* work together to keep the vehicle centered in its lane, enhancing safety during extended drives. Furthermore, the *Rear camera* provides a clear view of obstacles behind the vehicle, ensuring confident reversing. In critical situations, the *Brake assist* feature comes into play, boosting stopping power when needed most. Convenience features like the *Keyfob engine start control* enable you to start your car remotely, ensuring it’s comfortable and ready to go by the time you enter. In conclusion, the 2022 Honda Civic Sport excels in performance, safety, and innovative technology, making it an exceptional choice for anyone seeking a reliable and stylish compact car. With its comprehensive feature set, this vehicle is designed to meet the demands of modern drivers while providing peace of mind on the road. We want your trade in, even if you don't buy our vehicle. Call us today for a complimentary appraisal or Kelly Blue Book Instant Cash Offer.

You can connect with us by calling (619) 493-4787.*OTHER NOTABLE FEATURES AND OPTIONS YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT:*=== Safety and Security === * Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead. * Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision. * Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control. * Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, efficiency, and convenience in the 2022 Nissan Versa 1.6 SR. This captivating compact sedan is designed to elevate your driving experience and meet the demands of your modern lifestyle.

Boasting a sleek and sophisticated exterior, the Versa 1.6 SR commands attention with its striking Gray color and bold design elements. Alloy wheels and a sporty rear spoiler add a touch of athleticism, while the body-colored bumpers and power side mirrors with turn signal indicators lend an air of refinement.

Stepping inside, you'll be greeted by a well-appointed cabin that caters to your every need. Enjoy the comfort of the SR Fabric Seat Trim, with an available Armrest for added support. Stay connected and entertained with the seamless integration of Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, complemented by a premium audio system with 6 speakers.

Safety is a top priority in the Versa 1.6 SR, with a comprehensive suite of advanced features to give you peace of mind on the road. Rely on the Blind Spot Warning, Rear Parking Sensors, and Auto High-beam Headlights to help you navigate with confidence, while the ABS brakes, Dual front and side impact airbags, and Electronic Stability Control provide robust protection.

Efficiency is a hallmark of the Versa 1.6 SR, with an impressive EPA-estimated 32 city/40 highway MPG. The 1.6L 4-cylinder engine, paired with a smooth-shifting CVT transmission, delivers a responsive and fuel-sipping performance that will keep you on the road longer between fill-ups.

Experience the perfect blend of style, technology, and efficiency in the 2022 Nissan Versa 1.6 SR. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional compact sedan can elevate your driving experience.

description:
Discover the exceptional 2022 Honda Accord EX-L, a sophisticated and well-equipped sedan that combines style, performance, and advanced technology. This meticulously maintained vehicle is the perfect blend of practicality and refinement, offering a driving experience that will exceed your expectations.

Boasting a striking Black exterior, the Accord EX-L is more than just a beautiful car – it's a testament to Honda's commitment to engineering excellence. Under the hood, you'll find a 1.5T I4 DOHC 16V Turbocharged VTEC engine that delivers a remarkable balance of power and efficiency, with an impressive 30 city and 38 highway MPG.

Elevate your driving experience with the Accord EX-L's impressive list of features:

• 10 Speakers
• 450-Watt AM/FM/HD Premium Audio System
• Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control
• Heated Front Bucket Seats
• Perforated Leather Seat Trim
• Power Driver's Seat with Memory Function
• Blind Spot Information (BSI) System
• Collision Mitigation Braking System (CMBS) + FCW
• Lane Departure Warning System
• Adaptive Cruise Control with Low-Speed Follow

This vehicle is more than just a mode of transportation – it's a sanctuary on wheels, designed to keep you connected, comfortable, and safe. The spacious interior, with its premium materials and thoughtful touches, creates an environment that will make every journey a pleasure.

As you consider your next vehicle, we encourage you to experience the exceptional qualities of the 2022 Honda Accord EX-L. This sedan is a true testament to Honda's commitment to quality, innovation, and customer satisfaction. We're confident that once you take it for a test drive, you'll be captivated by its remarkable blend of style, performance, and technology.

We invite you to visit our showroom and discover the 2022 Honda Accord EX-L for yourself. Our knowledgeable sales team is ready to answer any questions you may have and guide you through the purchasing process. Experience the difference that this exceptional vehicle can make in your daily driving.

This 2022 Toyota Camry SE, has a Midnight Black Metallic exterior and Ash interior color with only 118,549 miles. Stock Number 750073A. You can connect with us by calling 619-350-4572. No Accidents! OTHER NOTABLE FEATURES AND OPTIONS YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT: Safety and Security
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

description: Overview Presenting a meticulously maintained 2022 Toyota Corolla Hybrid LE finished in classic White with a warm Tan interior — a smart, economical sedan designed for daily commuting and long drives alike. Powered by Toyota’s proven Hybrid Synergy Drive system combining a 1.8L Hybrid I4 gasoline engine and electric motor for a combined output of 121 hp, this Corolla Hybrid delivers outstanding fuel efficiency and a refined driving experience. EPA-rated at 53 MPG city and 52 MPG highway, it provides significant savings at the pump without sacrificing everyday usability or comfort. Powertrain and Driving Characteristics At the heart of this Corolla Hybrid LE is the 1.8-liter hybrid four-cylinder paired with an advanced electric drive system. The powertrain is managed through an electronically controlled continuously variable transmission (CVT), which contributes to smooth, linear acceleration and seamless transitions between electric and gasoline power. Regenerative braking recovers energy during deceleration to help recharge the hybrid battery, improving overall efficiency. The vehicle’s chassis tuning and suspension provide composed handling and a comfortable ride, ideal for urban commuting, highway cruising, and everything in between. Safety and Driver-Assist Features This Corolla LE comes factory-equipped with Toyota Safety Sense 2.0, a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies designed to enhance occupant protection and confidence behind the wheel. Key components include: - Pre-Collision System with Pedestrian Detection to help identify and mitigate frontal impacts - Full-Speed Range Dynamic Radar Cruise Control for more relaxed highway driving - Lane Departure Alert with Steering Assist to help keep the vehicle centered - Automatic High Beams for improved nighttime visibility - Road Sign Assist to help recognize certain traffic signs and display them on the instrument cluster In addition to Safety Sense, the vehicle includes Toyota’s Star Safety System, which integrates Vehicle Stability Control, Traction Control, Anti-lock Brake System (ABS), Electronic Brake-force Distribution (EBD), Brake Assist, and Smart Stop Technology. Complementing these systems are multiple airbags, a tire pressure monitoring system, and a backup camera for added convenience when maneuvering. Exterior Details The exterior features a crisp White finish that highlights the Corolla’s clean, contemporary lines. Factory lighting includes bright, efficient headlamps and LED daytime running lights for improved visibility and a modern appearance. The streamlined profile is complemented by aerodynamic styling cues that aid fuel economy. Factory wheels present a tasteful blend of durability and style, and body-color exterior trim and heated power mirrors (standard on many Corolla trims) add practical convenience. Overall, the exterior is in excellent condition, reflecting careful ownership and routine care. Interior Comfort and Practicality Inside, the Tan cloth-trimmed cabin offers a welcoming, airy atmosphere with thoughtful ergonomics and premium textures. The driver-focused cockpit features intuitive controls, a multi-information display providing key hybrid data and trip information, and a comfortably contoured driver’s seat with manual adjustments to support extended journeys. Rear passengers benefit from generous legroom and headroom for a compact sedan, and the 60/40 split-folding rear seatback expands cargo flexibility when longer items need to be carried. The Corolla sedan provides a practical trunk with ample volume for groceries, luggage, or gear. Technology and Connectivity The factory-installed infotainment system provides modern connectivity and convenience. Standard features include an easy-to-navigate touchscreen interface with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration to mirror smartphone apps and enable hands-free communication and media control. description: The 2022 Honda Accord Sport has recently seen a price drop of $203, making it an even more appealing option for those in the market for a midsize sedan. With this price reduction, potential buyers should act quickly to secure this remarkable vehicle before it’s gone! Under the hood, the Honda Accord Sport features a powerful 1.5L I-4 gasoline direct injection engine, delivering an impressive 192 horsepower paired with a continuously variable transmission CVT. This combination not only provides a spirited driving experience but also ensures excellent fuel efficiency, making it an ideal choice for both daily commutes and weekend getaways. One of the standout features of the 2022 Honda Accord Sport is its *smart device mirroring*. This innovative technology allows you to control your smartphone through the vehicles infotainment system, enabling you to access essential apps and music without taking your eyes off the road. It perfectly blends safety and convenience, enhancing your overall driving experience. Safety is a top priority in the Accord Sport, enhanced by features such as *lane departure prevention*. This system automatically keeps the vehicle centered in its lane, providing crucial protection against unintentional drifting. Coupled with *forward collision mitigation*, which actively monitors your surroundings and prepares your vehicle for potential impacts, you can drive confidently, knowing that your safety is prioritized. Additionally, the *front pedestrian impact prevention* system constantly scans the road for pedestrians, ensuring your vehicle can respond to potential hazards efficiently. The *rear camera* enhances your visibility while parking or reversing, allowing you to navigate tight spaces with ease. The 2022 Honda Accord Sport also boasts *adaptive cruise control with traffic stop-go*. This system maintains your desired speed while adjusting to the flow of traffic, automatically stopping and resuming speed as needed, making it perfect for both highway cruising and city driving. With features like *brake assist* for optimal stopping power and a user-friendly *touchscreen* interface, the Accord Sport is designed for modern drivers who value convenience and safety. If you’re seeking a vehicle that effortlessly combines style, efficiency, and advanced technology, the 2022 Honda Accord Sport stands out as an unbeatable option. Don’t miss out on this exceptional sedan act fast before its too late! We want your trade in, even if you don't buy our vehicle. Call us today for a complimentary appraisal or Kelly Blue Book Instant Cash Offer.

2022 Toyota Corolla XLE Sedan 4D - Now Available at Siry Motors in San DiegoLooking for a reliable, stylish, and feature-packed sedan? The 2022 Toyota Corolla XLE Sedan 4D is the perfect choice for drivers who demand both performance and comfort. Available now at Siry Motors in San Diego, California, this vehicle is designed to elevate your driving experience. Whether you're commuting to work or embarking on a weekend adventure, the Toyota Corolla XLE delivers exceptional value and modern conveniences.Stylish Design and Modern AestheticsThe 2022 Toyota Corolla XLE Sedan 4D features a sleek and aerodynamic design that turns heads wherever it goes. From its bold front grille to its sculpted body lines, this sedan exudes sophistication and confidence. The LED headlamps and daytime running lights not only enhance visibility but also add a touch of elegance to the vehicle's exterior. With premium wheels and a moon roof, the Corolla XLE combines functionality with a dash of luxury, making it a standout choice in its class.Powerful and Efficient PerformanceUnder the hood, the 2022 Toyota Corolla XLE is powered by a 1.8-liter, 4-cylinder engine paired with a smooth CVT automatic transmission. This combination delivers a perfect balance of power and efficiency, ensuring a responsive and enjoyable driving experience. The front-wheel-drive (FWD) system provides excellent traction and control, while features like Hill Start Assist Control and Vehicle Dynamic Control enhance stability on all types of terrain. Whether you're navigating city streets or cruising on the highway, the Corolla XLE offers a confident and composed ride.Advanced Safety Features for Peace of MindSafety is a top priority in the 2022 Toyota Corolla XLE Sedan 4D, and it comes equipped with an array of advanced safety technologies to keep you and your passengers protected. The Blind-Spot Monitor and Lane Departure Alert help you stay aware of your surroundings, while Dynamic Cruise Control ensures a safe distance from the vehicle ahead. The Corolla XLE also features multiple airbags, including dual front airbags, front and rear side airbags, knee airbags, and F&R head curtain airbags, for comprehensive protection in the event of a collision. With Safety Connect and Traction Control, you can drive with confidence knowing that you're equipped with cutting-edge safety innovations.Comfortable and Luxurious InteriorStep inside the 2022 Toyota Corolla XLE, and you'll find a thoughtfully designed cabin that prioritizes comfort and convenience. The heated seats provide warmth on chilly mornings, while the power-adjustable driver's seat allows you to find your ideal driving position. The spacious interior is complemented by high-quality materials and finishes, creating an inviting atmosphere for both driver and passengers. With features like keyless entry, push-button start, and a tilt & telescoping steering wheel, the Corolla XLE makes every journey more enjoyable.Innovative Technology for a Connected DriveThe Corolla XLE is packed with advanced technology to keep you connected and entertained on the road. The premium sound system delivers crystal-clear audio, while the AM/FM stereo, SiriusXM Satellite, and Bluetooth Wireless connectivity provide a variety of entertainment options. The backup camera makes parking and reversing a breeze, and the remote trunk release adds an extra layer of convenience. With the Preferred Accessory Package, you'll enjoy additional features that enhance your overall driving experience.Fuel Efficiency That Saves You MoneyOne of the standout features of the 2022 Toyota Corolla XLE Sedan 4D is its impressive fuel efficiency. Designed with eco-conscious drivers in mind, this sedan allows you to go further on every tank of gas. Whether you're running errands around San Diego or taking a road trip along the California coast, the Corolla XLE helps you save money at the pump without compromising on performance or comfort.Why Buy the 2022 Toyota Corolla XLE from Siry Motors in San Diego?At Siry Motors in San Diego, California, we pride ourselves on offering a wide selection of high-quality vehicles at competitive prices. The 2022 Toyota Corolla XLE Sedan 4D is no exception. Our knowledgeable and friendly team is here to help you find the perfect vehicle to suit your needs and budget. Conveniently located in San Diego, we make it easy for you to explore the Corolla XLE in person, take it for a test drive, and experience its exceptional features firsthand.Take the Next Step - Visit Siry Motors TodayDon't miss your chance to own the 2022 Toyota Corolla XLE Sedan 4D, a sedan that combines style, performance, and practicality in one exceptional package. Visit Siry Motors in San Diego, California, today to see this incredible vehicle for yourself. Our team is ready to assist you with any questions you may have and guide you through the car-buying process. Your dream car is waiting for you at Siry Motors!Contact UsReady to learn more about the 2022 Toyota Corolla XLE Sedan 4D? Contact Siry Motors in San Diego today to schedule a test drive or get more information. We look forward to helping you find the perfect vehicle for your lifestyle!```

Simulated suede/leather front seat upholstery gives the cabin a more upscale appearance and a pleasing tactile feel without the cost of genuine leather.

Adaptive Cruise Control: Adaptive Cruise Control (ACC) with Low-Speed Follow,Dual front impact airbags,Knee airbag,One Owner,Remote keyless entry,Tachometer,8 Speakers,Auto High-beam Headlights,Forward collision: Collision Mitigation Braking System (CMBS) + FCW mitigation,Passenger door bin,Power windows,ABS brakes,Outside temperature display,Panic alarm,Power door mirrors,Speed-sensing steering,Wheels: 18 Gloss Black Alloy,Rear window defroster,Delay-off headlights,Exterior Parking Camera Rear,Front Bucket Seats,Leather Shift Knob,New Tires,Serviced Here,New Brakes,Driver door bin,Local Trade,Speed control,Air Conditioning,Alloy wheels,Brake Plus® $699,Front anti-roll bar,Illuminated entry,Leather steering wheel,Trip computer,Dual front side impact airbags,Rear anti-roll bar,Telescoping steering wheel,Security system,Stargard $1295,4-Wheel Disc Brakes,Clean CarFax,Electronic Stability Control,Low tire pressure warning,Brake assist,Cloth Seat Trim,Four wheel independent suspension,Occupant sensing airbag,Power steering,Radio data system,Steering wheel mounted audio controls,Bumpers: body-color,Overhead airbag,Rear side impact airbag,Tilt steering wheel,Traction control,Apple CarPlay/Android Auto,Automatic temperature control,Driver vanity mirror,Emergency communication system: HondaLink,Front reading lights,Radio: 180-Watt AM/FM Audio System,AM/FM radio,Front Center Armrest,Fully automatic headlights,Passenger vanity mirror The 2022 Honda Civic Sport offers a compelling blend of sporty styling, enhanced features over the base model, and the core benefits of the Civic platform, including reliability, safety, and practicality.
Key benefits of the 2022 Honda Civic Sport include:
Performance & Driving Experience
Sporty Aesthetics & Feel: The Sport trim adds unique exterior elements like 18-inch gloss black alloy wheels, gloss black side mirrors, and a chrome exhaust finisher for a more aggressive look.
3-Mode Drive System: Drivers can tailor the car's performance with selectable ECON, Normal, and Sport modes, which adjust throttle response and steering feel.
Engaging Handling: It features a sport-tuned suspension and precise steering, contributing to a composed and fun-to-drive experience.
Paddle Shifters: Models with the Continuously Variable Transmission (CVT) include steering wheel-mounted paddle shifters, offering manual control over gear changes.
Technology & Convenience
Smart Entry with Walk Away Auto Lock®: This convenient feature automatically locks the vehicle when the driver walks away with the key fob and unlocks it upon approach.Remote Engine Start: Allows the driver to start the car remotely, a significant convenience feature.
Enhanced Infotainment: The Sport trim upgrades the audio system to 8 speakers (from the LX's 4) and includes a 7-inch color touchscreen display with standard Apple CarPlay® and Android Auto™ integration.
Comfort Upgrades: The interior features sport pedals and a leather-wrapped steering wheel and shift knob.
Safety & Reliability
Honda Sensing® Suite: A comprehensive suite of safety and driver-assistive technologies is standard, including Collision Mitigation Braking System™ (CMBS), Adaptive Cruise Control (ACC) with Low-Speed Follow, and Lane Keeping Assist System (LKAS).
High Safety Ratings: The 2022 Civic received high safety grades, thanks in part to new front airbags designed to reduce traumatic brain and neck injuries, and a reinforced body structure.
Dependable Engine: The Sport trim comes standard with the reliable 2.0L four-cylinder engine (158 horsepower), which many owners praise for its durability and longevity.
Practicality & Value
Fuel Efficiency: The Sport sedan delivers an EPA-estimated 30 city/37 highway MPG, making it an economical choice for daily commutes.
Spacious Interior: The cabin is roomy for a compact car, offering ample head and legroom for both front and rear passengers, and a generous cargo capacity of 14.8 cubic feet in the trunk.
Value for Money: Positioned as a mid-level trim, the Sport offers a significant step up in features and style over the base LX, at a competitive price point.

2022 Alfa Romeo Giulia Veloce RWD — 2L I-4 gasoline direct injection with MultiAir2 variable valve control, intercooled turbo delivering 280 HP paired to an 8-speed automatic, efficient on-road performance and respectable fuel economy for spirited drives and daily commuting. Recent market adjustments make this an opportune time to act—inventory and incentives are shifting, so book a test drive soon to lock in current pricing.

Quick Order Package 22U Veloce — This factory-selected package streamlines the buying process by bundling desirable performance and design upgrades so your Giulia arrives well-equipped and cohesive from day one.

Smart device mirroring brings your phone’s apps onto the Giulia’s display so you can access navigation, music and messaging more safely without fumbling with your device while driving.

Voice activated integrated navigation system lets you get turn-by-turn directions hands-free, keeping your focus on the road while the car guides you efficiently to your destination.

Keyfob vehicle start control lets you warm up or cool down the cabin remotely so you step into a comfortable interior no matter the weather.

Heated steering wheel provides quick, targeted warmth for chilly mornings so you can maintain a confident grip without bulky gloves.

The 2022 Tesla Model 3 RWD encapsulates the ideal fusion of cutting-edge technology and sleek automotive design, offering an unrivaled electric driving experience. Under its minimalist yet elegant exterior lies a robust electric motor that provides a seamless and almost silent acceleration, making every drive both exhilarating and eco-friendly. With the rear-wheel-drive configuration, drivers are treated to a dynamic and engaging handling experience, ensuring precise control around every curve and corner. The interior of the Model 3 is both futuristic and functional, dominated by a large touchscreen interface that serves as the command center for virtually all vehicle operations. Premium materials paired with a panoramic glass roof create an open and airy cabin feel. Space is utilized with incredible efficiency, offering ample room for passengers and generous storage options, making it perfectly suited for both daily commutes and longer journeys. Enhancing the driving experience further, the Model 3 is equipped with Tesla’s renowned Autopilot capabilities, bringing advanced driver assistance features to the forefront. Charging infrastructure is a cornerstone of the Tesla ecosystem, with convenient access to Tesla's Supercharger network ensuring that the Model 3 is ready for any adventure. The vehicle's energy efficiency extends the range considerably, minimizing the need for frequent charging stops and allowing for travel with confidence. Safety is paramount, and the Model 3 includes a suite of sensors and cameras designed to protect its occupants and assist the driver. Overall, the 2022 Tesla Model 3 RWD stands as a beacon of innovation in the automotive world, pushing boundaries while delivering a comfortable, efficient, and engaging driving experience. description:
Discover the exhilaration of driving the 2022 BMW 2 Series 228i. This dynamic and well-appointed coupe offers a thrilling blend of performance, technology, and style that will captivate the senses.

Boasting a powerful 2.0L 4-cylinder engine and an 8-speed automatic transmission, the 2 Series delivers an exceptional driving experience with impressive fuel efficiency. Enjoy an EPA-estimated 24 MPG in the city and 34 MPG on the highway, making this BMW an exceptional value.

• Accident Free Carfax History
• Panoramic Moonroof
• Wheels: 18" x 8.0" Multi-Spoke Bi-Color
• Live Cockpit Pro w/Navi
• Lights Package
• Universal Garage-Door Opener

The 2 Series is equipped with a host of premium features that elevate every journey. Indulge in the convenience of keyless entry, the comfort of heated front seats, and the connectivity of Apple CarPlay and Android Auto. The panoramic moonroof floods the cabin with natural light, creating an open and airy atmosphere.

Designed with the driver in mind, the 2 Series offers a wealth of advanced safety technologies, including adaptive LED headlights, a rearview camera, and a suite of driver-assist features. You'll also enjoy the confidence of a four-wheel independent suspension and speed-sensitive steering, ensuring a poised and responsive ride.

Step inside the 2 Series and discover the perfect blend of luxury and sportiness. The cabin is appointed with high-quality materials, including SensaTec upholstery and a sleek, driver-focused cockpit. The intuitive infotainment system and 10-speaker audio system provide endless entertainment and seamless connectivity.

Whether you're seeking a dynamic daily driver or a thrilling weekend companion, the 2022 BMW 2 Series 228i is the perfect choice. Experience the unparalleled joy of BMW ownership and schedule a test drive today. We're confident you'll be captivated by this exceptional coupe.

Discover the perfect blend of style, performance, and technology in the 2022 Nissan Sentra SV. This exceptional sedan boasts a sleek silver exterior that turns heads wherever you go. Powered by a 2.0L DOHC engine and CVT with Xtronic, the Sentra SV delivers an impressive 29 city/39 highway MPG, making it an exceptional choice for the savvy driver.

Key features include:
• Carpeted Floor Mats w/Trunk Mat

Elevate your driving experience with the advanced technology and premium amenities of the Sentra SV. Enjoy seamless connectivity with NissanConnect featuring Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, while the Blind Spot Warning and Rear Parking Sensors provide added peace of mind. The spacious interior with Premium Cloth Seat Trim and Split Folding Rear Seat offers exceptional comfort and versatility.

Safety is paramount in the Sentra SV, with features like Dual Front Impact Airbags, Dual Front Side Impact Airbags, Knee Airbag, and Electronic Stability Control ensuring your protection on the road. The 4-Wheel Disc Brakes with ABS and Brake Assist provide confident stopping power, while the Four Wheel Independent Suspension and Speed-Sensing Steering deliver a smooth and responsive driving experience.

Discover the perfect balance of style, technology, and safety in the 2022 Nissan Sentra SV. This exceptional sedan is ready to elevate your driving experience and exceed your expectations. Visit our showroom today to take a test drive and see why the Sentra SV should be your next vehicle.

description: Discover modern style, impressive performance and everyday practicality in this 2022 Honda Accord Sedan Sport SE, now available at BMW of Monrovia. As one of the most celebrated midsize sedans on the market, the Accord Sport SE stands out for its refined driving dynamics, advanced features and exceptional value. Designed for drivers who want a sleek, sporty look paired with reliable capability, this Accord offers a well-rounded experience ideal for commuting, family travel or weekend outings throughout Southern California.Under the hood, the Accord Sport SE delivers smooth, responsive power that makes daily driving more enjoyable. Its finely tuned suspension and precise steering contribute to a confident, dynamic feel on city streets, winding foothill roads and busy Los Angeles freeways. Whether you're merging into traffic, cruising along scenic routes or navigating tight parking areas, the Accord provides a composed and engaging ride that enhances every journey.Inside, the Accord Sport SE offers a welcoming cabin crafted with comfort and convenience in mind. Supportive seating, intuitive controls and thoughtful design details elevate the driving experience. Advanced infotainment technology ensures seamless access to navigation, entertainment and smartphone connectivity, allowing you to stay informed and entertained wherever you go. With generous passenger space and a roomy trunk, the Accord adapts easily to daily responsibilities---whether you're carrying groceries, sports gear or weekend luggage.The Sport SE trim adds premium touches and enhanced features that bring even more value to the Accord lineup. From its stylish appointments to its advanced comfort elements, this model offers a refined atmosphere that complements its sporty character. Additionally, Honda's reputation for long-term dependability provides peace of mind for drivers seeking a sedan they can trust year after year.With its blend of efficiency, comfort, style and performance, the 2022 Honda Accord Sedan Sport SE continues to be a compelling choice for drivers who want sophistication without compromising practicality.Visit BMW of Monrovia located at 1425 S Mountain Ave, Monrovia, CA 91016 today.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of rugged capability and modern convenience with the 2024 Toyota Tacoma SR. This exceptional mid-size truck is ready to take on any adventure, whether you're conquering the trails or navigating the city streets.

Boasting a comprehensive list of impressive features, the Tacoma SR is the ultimate companion for your active lifestyle. Enjoy the convenience of:

• Android Auto and Apple CarPlay
• Backup Camera
• Bluetooth Connectivity
• Carfax 1-Owner

This Toyota Certified vehicle has undergone a rigorous 160-point inspection, ensuring it meets the highest standards of quality and performance. With a Powertrain Limited Warranty of 84 months/100,000 miles and a 12-month/12,000-mile Limited Comprehensive Warranty, you can drive with confidence, knowing your investment is protected.

The Tacoma SR's 2.4L 4-cylinder engine, paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission and 4-wheel drive, delivers an impressive balance of power and efficiency. Achieving up to 24 mpg on the highway, this truck is designed to take you further, whether you're hauling gear or navigating the open road.

Exterior features like the body-color bumpers and rear step bumper complement the Tacoma's rugged good looks, while the 17-inch steel wheels and variably intermittent wipers provide both style and functionality. Inside, the split-folding rear seat, front bucket seats, and front center armrest offer exceptional comfort and versatility.

Safety is a top priority, with features like dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, and electronic stability control ensuring your peace of mind on every journey.

As a Toyota Certified Used Vehicle, this Tacoma SR comes with the added benefits of a 160-point inspection, roadside assistance, and a transferable warranty. You can trust that this truck has been meticulously maintained and is ready to provide years of reliable service.

Don't miss your chance to experience the uncompromising capability and modern amenities of the 2024 Toyota Tacoma SR. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional truck can enhance your driving experience.
