2006 Honda Civic LX:

Dependable and fuel-efficient sedan known for its longevity and easy drivability. Powered by a reliable 4-cylinder engine paired with a smooth automatic transmission, the Civic delivers excellent fuel economy and a comfortable ride. Its compact size makes it easy to maneuver while still providing a stable and confident driving experience.

Inside, the Civic LX offers a simple and functional cabin with comfortable cloth seating, power windows and locks, cruise control, and an easy-to-use audio system. The interior layout is practical and ergonomic, providing good visibility and ample space for both front and rear passengers, along with a usable trunk for everyday needs.

Renowned for reliability and low cost of ownership, the Civic has long been a smart choice for commuters, first-time drivers, or anyone seeking dependable transportation. Combining efficiency, comfort, and proven Honda engineering, this 2006 Honda Civic LX is a solid and practical sedan you can count on.

Experience the pinnacle of capability and innovation with this 2024 GMC Sierra 1500 AT4X. This remarkable vehicle is a testament to GMC's commitment to engineering excellence, offering a seamless blend of power, technology, and premium features that will elevate your driving experience.

• Bose Premium Series w/12-Speaker System
• MultiPro Tailgate Audio System by Kicker (LPO)
• SiriusXM w/360L
• Steering Wheel Audio Controls
• Wireless Charging
• Heated 2nd Row Outboard Seats
• Heated Driver & Front Outboard Passenger Seating
• Ventilated Driver & Front Passenger Seats
• Hitch View
• In-Vehicle Trailering System App
• Integrated Trailer Brake Controller
• Trailer Tire Pressure Monitor System

Beneath the bold, commanding exterior lies a heart of pure power. The EcoTec3 6.2L V8 engine, paired with a 10-Speed Automatic transmission and 4WD, delivers exceptional performance and capability, ensuring you can conquer any terrain with confidence. With a best-in-class towing capacity and a suite of advanced trailering technologies, this Sierra 1500 AT4X is the ultimate companion for your most ambitious adventures.

Step inside and experience the epitome of luxury and convenience. The cabin is meticulously crafted, with premium materials and a wealth of cutting-edge features that cater to your every need. The Bose Premium Series audio system, with its 12 high-performance speakers, will immerse you in a captivating soundscape, while the MultiPro Tailgate Audio System by Kicker provides the perfect soundtrack for your outdoor activities.

Connectivity is seamlessly integrated, with wireless Apple CarPlay, wireless Android Auto, and a Wi-Fi Hotspot, ensuring you stay connected on the go. The Multicolor 15" Diagonal Head-Up Display puts vital information right in your line of sight, allowing you to keep your focus on the road ahead.

Safety is paramount, and this Sierra 1500 AT4X is equipped with a suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including Rear Cross Traffic Braking, Rear Pedestrian Detection, and Ultrasonic Front & Rear Park Assist, providing you with the confidence and peace of mind you deserve.

Whether you're tackling the great outdoors or navigating the urban jungle, this 2024 GMC Sierra 1500 AT4X is the ultimate expression of power, capability, and refinement. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by what this remarkable vehicle has to offer.

Vehicle Details
Discover the ultimate heavy-duty truck ready to conquer work and weekend adventures — a 2022 Chevrolet Silverado 2500 LTZ 4WD with the powerful V8 6.6L Duramax Diesel. Located in Fort Payne, AL, this Chevrolet Silverado delivers commanding performance, exceptional towing capability, and premium comfort at the best price in the area. CARFAX 1-Owner history gives added confidence in its care and maintenance. Inside, enjoy luxurious leather seats, automatic climate control, and a driver-focused cabin packed with convenience. Steering wheel audio controls keep your focus on the road while managing music and calls. Advanced safety features include Lane Departure Warning to help prevent unintentional lane drift and enhance long-haul confidence. The robust diesel V8 provides impressive torque for towing trailers, hauling heavy loads, and tackling rough terrain with 4WD capability. This LTZ trim blends capability with upscale touches: durable bed space, modern infotainment, and thoughtful driver-assist technology. Whether you need reliable worksite performance, comfortable daily driving, or a weekend towing rig, this Chevrolet Silverado 2500 LTZ checks every box. Located in Fort Payne, AL, and priced to move — this is the best-priced, best-maintained 2022 Chevrolet Silverado 2500 LTZ V8 6.6L Diesel available locally. Contact us to schedule a test drive and see why this CARFAX 1-Owner Chevrolet Silverado is the smart choice for power, comfort, and value.

Equipment
This 2022 Chevrolet Silverado 2500 features steering wheel audio controls. Our dealership has already run the CARFAX report and it is clean. A clean CARFAX is a great asset for resale value in the future. Keep your hands warm all winter with a heated steering wheel in this 2022 Chevrolet Silverado 2500 . Never get into a cold vehicle again with the remote start feature on the Chevrolet Silverado. This 2022 Chevrolet Silverado 2500 features a hands-free Bluetooth phone system. See what's behind you with the back up camera on this Chevrolet Silverado. This vehicle offers Automatic Climate Control for personalized comfort. The leather seats in the Chevrolet Silverado are a must for buyers looking for comfort, durability, and style. This Chevrolet Silverado's Lane Departure Warning keeps you safe by alerting you when you drift from your lane. An off-road package is installed on this unit so you are ready for your four-wheeling best.

description:
Discover the unparalleled power and refined luxury of this 2022 Ram 2500 Limited. With its commanding presence and meticulously crafted interior, this exceptional vehicle is poised to elevate your driving experience to new heights.

Key features include:
• Limited Level 1 Equipment Group
• Auto Level Rear Air Suspension
• Tri-Fold Tonneau Cover
• Anti-Spin Differential Rear Axle
• MOPAR Deployable Bed Step

The 6.4L V8 engine, paired with the 8-speed automatic transmission and 4WD, delivers the muscle you need to conquer any terrain. Indulge in the premium sound of the 17-speaker harman/kardon system, while the surround-view camera and adaptive cruise control ensure a seamless, confident ride.

Designed to impress, this Ram 2500 Limited boasts a striking Delmonico Red Pearlcoat exterior and a meticulously appointed cabin that exudes sophistication. Heated and ventilated front seats, a heated steering wheel, and a digital rearview mirror are just a few of the luxurious touches that elevate your driving experience.

Backed by the Ram Certified Pre-Owned Gold program, this vehicle has undergone a rigorous 125-point inspection and comes with a comprehensive warranty, roadside assistance, and a thorough reconditioning process using authentic Mopar parts. You can trust that this Ram 2500 Limited is a true gem, ready to provide you with unparalleled performance, comfort, and peace of mind.

Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional truck your own. Schedule a test drive today and experience the power and refinement of the 2022 Ram 2500 Limited.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, efficiency, and versatility with this 2017 Ford Focus SE. This exceptional compact car is ready to elevate your driving experience and exceed your expectations.

• Equipment Group 200A

Boasting an impressive EcoBoost 1.0L I3 GTDi DOHC Turbocharged VCT engine, this Focus SE delivers an exceptional balance of power and fuel efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 30 city/40 highway MPG. The 6-speed manual transmission provides a responsive and engaging driving experience, putting you in full control.

Exterior-wise, the Focus SE's striking gold color commands attention, complemented by its sleek and aerodynamic design. Step inside and you'll be greeted by a well-appointed interior, featuring cloth front bucket seats, a split-folding rear seat, and a SYNC communications and entertainment system, ensuring both comfort and connectivity.

Equipped with a host of advanced safety features, including dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, an emergency communication system, and electronic stability control, this Focus SE prioritizes your well-being on the road. The rear parking camera and traction control further enhance your confidence behind the wheel.

Convenience is key, and this Focus SE delivers with power windows, remote keyless entry, steering wheel-mounted audio controls, and a rear window defroster. The 16-inch painted aluminum wheels and exterior parking camera rear add a touch of sophistication to the overall package.

Whether you're commuting, running errands, or embarking on a weekend adventure, this 2017 Ford Focus SE is ready to rise to the occasion. Experience the perfect blend of style, efficiency, and technology that this exceptional compact car has to offer. Contact us today to schedule a test drive and discover why the Focus SE should be your next vehicle.

This 2010 Toyota Corolla LE is a reliable and well-equipped compact car that offers exceptional value. With its sleek gray exterior and a spacious, well-appointed interior, this Corolla is the perfect choice for the savvy driver seeking a practical and dependable vehicle.

• Fully serviced and fresh PA State Inspection
• Auto Reward Program
• Great service history
• LE Extra Value Package #1
• Remote keyless entry with panic switch
• Cruise control

Under the hood, this Corolla is powered by a 1.8L I4 DOHC Dual VVT-i engine, delivering a smooth and efficient driving experience. With an EPA-estimated 26 mpg in the city and 34 mpg on the highway, this Corolla ensures you'll spend less time and money at the pump.

The interior of this Corolla LE is designed with your comfort and convenience in mind. Enjoy features such as air conditioning, a CD player, and a rear window defroster to keep you comfortable year-round. The split-folding rear seat and ample cargo space provide the flexibility to accommodate your ever-changing needs, whether you're running errands or embarking on a road trip.

Safety is paramount, and this Corolla is equipped with a suite of advanced safety features, including dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, and electronic stability control. You can drive with confidence, knowing that you and your passengers are well-protected.

This Corolla LE is an exceptional value in the compact car market. With its proven reliability, impressive fuel efficiency, and comprehensive list of features, it's the perfect choice for the savvy buyer seeking a dependable and practical vehicle. We invite you to come in and experience the Corolla for yourself. This vehicle is available as-is, so don't miss your chance to make it your own.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, performance, and technology in this 2019 Volkswagen Jetta 1.4T S. With its sleek black exterior and well-appointed interior, this compact sedan is the ideal choice for the discerning driver.

Boasting an impressive array of features, this Jetta is equipped to elevate your driving experience. Enjoy the convenience of the Exterior Parking Camera Rear, the added safety of Delay-off headlights and Panic alarm, and the enhanced control of Speed control. The alloy wheels and 16" Silver Rama wheels lend a touch of sophistication, while the 1.4L TSI engine and 8-Speed Automatic with Tiptronic transmission deliver a responsive and efficient performance.

• Exterior Parking Camera Rear
• Delay-off headlights
• Panic alarm
• Speed control
• Alloy wheels
• Wheels: 16" Silver Rama

Beyond these standout features, this Jetta is packed with a wealth of amenities to enhance your daily commute. With air conditioning, power windows, and remote keyless entry, you'll enjoy a comfortable and convenient driving experience. The Composition Color touchscreen infotainment system with AM/FM radio and speed-sensing steering further elevate the in-cabin experience.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like ABS brakes, dual front impact airbags, and Electronic Stability Control providing you and your passengers with added peace of mind. The front bucket seats and split folding rear seat offer versatility and comfort, while the tilt and telescoping steering wheel allow for a customized driving position.

Whether you're navigating the city streets or embarking on a road trip, this 2019 Volkswagen Jetta 1.4T S is the perfect companion. With an EPA-estimated 30 mpg in the city and 40 mpg on the highway, you'll enjoy exceptional fuel efficiency and the freedom to explore.

We invite you to experience the exceptional craftsmanship and attention to detail that define this Jetta. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this vehicle can elevate your driving experience. We're confident that once you take it for a test drive, you'll be convinced that this is the perfect car for you.

Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2022 Ford F-150 Lariat. This powerful and versatile pickup boasts a bold presence on the road, combined with a refined and well-appointed interior that caters to your every need.

Highlighted features include:
• LOCAL TRADE
• NON SMOKER

Under the hood, this F-150 Lariat is equipped with a potent 3.5L V6 EcoBoost engine, delivering impressive power and efficiency. The 10-speed automatic transmission and 4-wheel drive system ensure seamless performance, whether you're navigating city streets or tackling rugged terrain.

The exterior of this F-150 Lariat commands attention with its striking Black paint and chrome accents. The LARIAT CHROME APPEARANCE PACKAGE elevates the look with features like chrome front tow hooks, a chrome single-tip exhaust, and 18-inch chrome-like PVD wheels. The TWIN PANEL MOONROOF allows you to enjoy the great outdoors from the comfort of your cabin.

Step inside, and you'll be surrounded by a wealth of premium amenities. The BLACK, LEATHER-TRIMMED BUCKET SEATS offer unparalleled comfort and support, with both heating and ventilation functions. The EQUIPMENT GROUP 501A MID upgrades the audio experience with the renowned B&O Sound System by Bang & Olufsen, while the UNIVERSAL GARAGE DOOR OPENER and ONBOARD 400W OUTLET provide added convenience.

For those who tow, the TRAILER TOW PACKAGE equips this F-150 Lariat with a Class IV trailer hitch receiver, an integrated trailer brake controller, and Pro Trailer Backup Assist, making hitching and maneuvering a breeze. The 360 DEGREE CAMERA further enhances your confidence behind the wheel, providing a comprehensive view of your surroundings.

With its impressive capabilities, premium features, and striking appearance, this 2022 Ford F-150 Lariat is the ultimate expression of power and refinement. Experience the difference for yourself by scheduling a test drive at our showroom today. We're confident you'll be impressed by the uncompromising quality and exceptional value this vehicle delivers.

description:
Discover the perfect balance of style, comfort, and efficiency in this 2019 Nissan Sentra SV. With its sleek red exterior and well-appointed interior, this Sentra is ready to elevate your driving experience.

• SUPER LOW MILES
• BLUETOOTH WIRELESS/HANDS FREE
• USB PORTS
• NON-SMOKER
• PUSH BUTTON IGNITION
• KEYLESS ENTRY
• FUEL EFFICIENT WITH PLENTY OF POWER
• CLEAN CARFAX
• Special Edition Package
• Blind Spot Warning (BSW)
• Rear Cross Traffic Alert (RCTA)
• Intelligent Cruise Control (ICC)
• Power Sliding Glass Moonroof w/Tilt Feature
• Rear Disc Brakes

Powered by a 1.8L 4-cylinder engine and equipped with a continuously variable transmission, this Sentra delivers an impressive 29 MPG in the city and 37 MPG on the highway, making it an exceptional choice for your daily commute or weekend getaways. The special edition package adds a touch of sophistication with 17-inch alloy wheels, a dual-zone automatic climate control system, and a premium audio system with SiriusXM radio.

Step inside and you'll be greeted by a spacious, well-designed cabin that offers ample room for you and your passengers. The supportive, six-way adjustable driver's seat and tilt/telescoping steering wheel ensure a comfortable and customized driving position. Enjoy the convenience of keyless entry, push-button start, and a rear-view camera, all while staying connected with the available Bluetooth and USB ports.

Safety is a top priority in this Sentra, with features like dual front and side impact airbags, antilock brakes, and electronic stability control providing a secure and confident driving experience. The rear cross-traffic alert and blind spot warning systems further enhance your awareness on the road, giving you peace of mind during every journey.

This 2019 Nissan Sentra SV is a remarkable blend of style, technology, and efficiency. With its impressive list of features and low mileage, this vehicle is an exceptional value that is sure to impress. Visit our showroom today to experience the Sentra's exceptional capabilities for yourself.

This 2021 Jeep Gladiator Sport is a rugged and capable off-road adventure vehicle that's ready to tackle any challenge. Powered by a robust 3.6L V6 24V VVT engine paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission, this Gladiator delivers impressive performance and 4WD capability. The oversized off-road tires and Max Tow Package with 4.10 axle ratio provide unparalleled traction and hauling capacity, making this Jeep the perfect companion for your outdoor pursuits.

The Gladiator's unique design blends the utility of a truck with the off-road prowess of a Jeep, resulting in a truly versatile and capable vehicle. The Dana M210 wide front axle and Dana M220 wide rear axle, coupled with the anti-spin differential and heavy-duty brakes, ensure exceptional handling and control both on and off the beaten path. The 240-amp alternator and heavy-duty engine cooling further enhance the Gladiator's performance and reliability.

Exterior features like the black molded-in-color fender flares and the MOPAR spray-in bedliner add both style and functionality, while the Daytime Running Lamp System and trailer hitch zoom provide added convenience and safety. Inside, you'll find a well-appointed cabin with a range of technology and comfort features, including the Uconnect 3 infotainment system, air conditioning, and power steering.

Whether you're planning a weekend getaway, tackling rugged terrain, or hauling heavy loads, this 2021 Jeep Gladiator Sport is the perfect companion. Experience the uncompromising capability and versatility that only a Jeep can deliver.

Here at Reed-Lallier Chevrolet we have a No Haggle pricing policy on all of our pre-owned vehicles. We price our vehicles very competitively in the market to give you an extremely fair price right up front. We do not negotiate on the price of the vehicle. Most of our cars are priced at thousands below NADA retail value. We have taken many things into consideration when pricing the cars, exterior condition, miles, interior condition and warranty to name a few. Our cars are priced in the condition that you see them. As with any used vehicle, they have been driven on the road, parked in garages and parking lots and driven through all kinds of weather. Some wear and tear is normal. This may include some small scratches or door dings, interior wear, chips in the windshield etc. We have taken all of these into consideration and priced the vehicles accordingly. All vehicles must pass North Carolina State inspection. Cars come with one key unless otherwise noted or disclosed. Not all cars have second keys. Not all cars have owners manuals. We will be happy to price any parts or repairs that you may desire at our wholesale cost and include them in the deal and in your financing. We have GM Certified vehicles here on the lot, they come with a factory backed extended limited warranty (see dealer for details). Some of our vehicles are still covered under the original factory warranty and are therefore sold with the balance of that warranty in place. Some of our vehicles are sold AS-IS, this means that the buyer is responsible for all repairs. Some vehicles will have open recalls, we will provide all paperwork and disclose any recalls to you before purchase.

description:
Discover the exceptional 2015 Acura TLX V6 Tech, a masterful blend of style, performance, and cutting-edge technology. This sophisticated sedan is poised to elevate your driving experience and exceed your expectations.

Boasting a striking black exterior, the TLX V6 Tech commands attention with its sleek and dynamic silhouette. Beneath the hood, a powerful 3.5L V6 SOHC VTEC 24V engine, paired with a smooth-shifting 9-speed automatic transmission, delivers an exhilarating and efficient performance, achieving an impressive 21 MPG in the city and 34 MPG on the highway.

• Navigation System
• 10 Speakers
• Premium audio system: Acura/ELS Surround
• Dual-zone automatic climate control
• Heated front seats
• Power moonroof
• Rearview camera
• Blind spot monitoring
• Adaptive cruise control
• Lane departure warning

Indulge in the exceptional comfort and convenience of the TLX V6 Tech. The cabin is meticulously crafted with premium Milano perforated leather-trimmed seats, providing a luxurious and supportive driving experience. The intuitive infotainment system, complete with a premium Acura/ELS Studio audio system, keeps you connected and entertained on every journey.

Experience the unparalleled handling and responsiveness of the TLX V6 Tech, thanks to its sophisticated four-wheel independent suspension and speed-sensing power steering. The advanced safety features, including airbags, anti-lock brakes, and electronic stability control, work in harmony to provide you and your passengers with the utmost protection.

This exceptional Acura TLX V6 Tech is a testament to the brand's commitment to excellence. With its impressive performance, cutting-edge technology, and refined craftsmanship, it's the perfect choice for the discerning driver who demands the very best.

We invite you to visit our showroom and experience the 2015 Acura TLX V6 Tech for yourself. Let us demonstrate how this exceptional sedan can elevate your driving experience and exceed your expectations. Contact us today to schedule a test drive and discover the joy of owning this remarkable vehicle.

description: Maximize your daily commute with the 2015 Chevrolet Sonic LTZ. Dressed in the sophisticated Ashen Gray Metallic, this sedan is the perfect choice for drivers who want a "fun-to-drive" subcompact that doesn't skimp on premium features. Under the hood, the 1.4L Turbocharged engine provides a spirited 138 horsepower and 148 lb-ft of torque, giving you plenty of "get-up-and-go" for highway merging while maintaining an impressive 37 MPG on the highway.As the top-tier LTZ trim, this Sonic offers a surprisingly upscale interior for its class. You'll find perforated leatherette seating with heated front seats to keep you comfortable during chilly Arkansas mornings. The leather-wrapped sport steering wheel and Chevrolet MyLink 7-inch color touchscreen provide a modern, tech-focused cockpit, while the premium 6-speaker audio system ensures your favorite playlists sound great every mile of the way.Safety and convenience are standard in this well-equipped sedan. The Exterior Parking Camera takes the stress out of tight parking spots, and the comprehensive 10-airbag system provides peace of mind for you and your passengers. With remote keyless entry, front fog lights, and heated door mirrors, this Sonic handles the small details of your day with ease.At the Superior Pre-Owned Superstore of Bentonville, we believe in a car-buying experience that is faster, simpler, and more transparent. We've meticulously cleaned and serviced this Ashen Gray Sonic to ensure its ready to provide reliable, efficient service for its next owner. Visit us today to experience the uncommonly candid and respectful service that has made us Arkansas' trusted choice for over 30 years.

• Sport Line

This 2015 BMW 3 Series 328i is a true driver's car, blending exhilarating performance, sophisticated design, and an impressive array of premium features. description:
This 2015 Kia Optima LX is a sleek and sophisticated sedan that offers exceptional value and a wealth of premium features. With its striking black exterior, this Optima commands attention on the road, while the refined interior provides a comfortable and well-equipped driving experience.

• Aurora Black exterior
• 17" alloy wheels
• Rear bumper applique
• 6 speakers
• SiriusXM radio
• CD player
• Air conditioning
• Power windows and locks
• Remote keyless entry
• Steering wheel-mounted audio controls
• 4-wheel independent suspension
• ABS brakes
• Dual front and side impact airbags
• Electronic stability control

Under the hood, the Optima is powered by a 2.4L I4 DGI DOHC engine paired with a 6-speed automatic transmission with Sportmatic. This efficient powertrain delivers an impressive 23 MPG in the city and 34 MPG on the highway, making it an excellent choice for your daily commute or weekend getaways.

The Optima's well-appointed interior features premium cloth seating, a split-folding rear seat, and a center console with armrest for added comfort and convenience. The intuitive dashboard layout and user-friendly controls make it easy to stay connected and in control while on the road.

Safety is a top priority in the Optima, with features like dual front and side impact airbags, ABS brakes, and electronic stability control providing peace of mind behind the wheel. The vehicle's four-wheel independent suspension and speed-sensing steering ensure a smooth and responsive driving experience.

Whether you're looking for a practical and efficient daily driver or a stylish and well-equipped sedan, this 2015 Kia Optima LX is an exceptional choice. Experience the perfect blend of performance, comfort, and technology by scheduling a test drive today.

What is Wholesale Open to Public? Derrow Shirkey Ford's Wholesale Open to Public is a select offering of used cars that have traditionally been sold at the auction to independent dealers and small used car lots. These are vehicles that fall outside of Derrow Shirkey Ford's used car guidelines. They are generally higher mileage, older, lower-priced vehicles that are perhaps 'flawed' in some way. Some general guidelines for a wholesale vehicle: • They are sold without a warranty • They are offered for a limited time only - 30 days • They are sold 100% AS-IS without any warranty coverage • They are sold with our "best price" posted on the windshield. There is no negotiation necessary. Why Wholesale Open to Public? Simply put - our customers have requested that we make these vehicles available. Many of our customers have a need for basic transportation. By offering a broader selection of "kid's cars", 2nd car, college cars, and other inexpensive transportation options, we feel we can better serve our current customers and the general market.

We are located 2 miles South of the turnpike at exit 13. Our location makes it a very simple drive from Toledo, Fort Wayne, Hillsdale, Angola, Bryan, Defiance, Napoleon, or Jackson. OUR MISSION STATEMENT- We will be honest and transparent. Through teamwork, honesty and hard work, we will build trusting relationships with our customers, always striving to exceed their expectations. The same holds true for our team members as we constantly learn and improve from within ourselves and each other. Come see for yourself why Derrow-Shirkey Ford Lincoln is the fastest growing dealership in the tri-state area. We are committed to making the car buying experience fast, fun and easy!!! 1. Pricing - We post our best price on every vehicle, every day. Period. 2. Trade In’s - We’ll make you a cash offer. No-Nonsense. We will buy your vehicle regardless if you purchase from us or not. 3. Financing - Multiple quotes in minutes. 4. No Surprises - We will gladly provide a history report and a copy of any repairs we performed on the vehicle. 5. Long Distance, No Problem! - We sell vehicles from New York to California.

Boasting an impressive array of features, this Jetta is equipped to enhance your driving experience. Highlights include:

• 6 Speakers
• SiriusXM Radio
• CD Player
• Air Conditioning
• Rear Window Defroster
• Power Driver Seat
• Remote Keyless Entry
• Traction Control

Powered by a 1.8L I4 DOHC engine and paired with a smooth-shifting 6-speed automatic transmission, this Jetta delivers a responsive and efficient performance, with an EPA-estimated 25 city/36 highway mpg. The front-wheel-drive system provides confident handling, while the independent suspension ensures a comfortable and composed ride, even on longer journeys.

Step inside the Jetta and you'll be greeted by a well-designed, spacious cabin that exudes quality. description: Discover the Perfect Blend of Style and Safety with the 2020 Hyundai Elantra SE in Striking Calypso Red For those who appreciate a harmonious balance of style, performance, and safety, the 2020 Hyundai Elantra SE stands out as a compelling choice. Its sleek Calypso Red exterior not only turns heads but also complements the vehicle s dynamic design. Under the hood, the efficient 2.0L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine paired with a CVT transmission ensures a smooth and responsive driving experience, perfect for urban commutes or weekend getaways. Safety is paramount, with features like Lane Keeping Assist and Front Collision Mitigation providing peace of mind on every journey. The Elantra SE is equipped with a comprehensive suite of airbags, including knee and side airbags, enhancing protection for all passengers. Inside, the intuitive Bluetooth Connection and Steering Wheel Audio Controls offer seamless connectivity and entertainment options, making every drive enjoyable. With its Back-Up Camera, maneuvering in tight spaces becomes effortless, while the Keyless Entry system adds a layer of convenience to your daily routine. Whether you re navigating city streets or cruising the open road, the Hyundai Elantra SE is designed to meet the needs of modern drivers who value innovation and reliability. Be sure to call or visit Reliable Cars to discover more. Your new favorite vehicle awaits - don't let someone else drive it home!

Experience the 2020 Ford Fusion Titanium for yourself and elevate your daily drive. Visit our dealership today and take one for a test drive. You won't be disappointed.

**LOCAL TRADE**, **POWER MOONROOF/SUNROOF, **LEATHER SEATING**, **HEATED/COOLED SEATS**, **HEATED STEERING WHEEL**, Auto High-beam Headlights, Automatic temperature control, Exterior Parking Camera Rear, Four wheel independent suspension, Front dual zone A/C, Front fog lights, Fully automatic headlights, Memory seat, Navigation System, Power driver seat, Rain sensing wipers, Remote keyless entry, Speed-sensing steering, Steering wheel mounted audio controls, SYNC 3 Communications & Entertainment System, Wheels: 18" Premium-Painted Aluminum.

Sliding into the 2020 Ford Fusion Hybrid Titanium feels like stepping into a vehicle that effortlessly supports your day, from early morning commutes to evening errands. Its serene cabin and smooth acceleration create a sense of calm confidence, turning rush-hour traffic into a more relaxed part of the routine. The hybrid powertrain quietly blends efficiency with responsiveness, letting you glide through city streets and open roads with ease. With comfortable seating and intuitive controls always within reach, each drive becomes a balance of comfort and practicality that fits naturally into everyday life.

The Titanium trim elevates the Fusion Hybrid with refined touches and advanced features that enhance both comfort and capability. Its efficient hybrid system pairs a responsive gasoline engine with electric assist to deliver strong fuel economy without sacrificing smooth, steady performance. Inside, premium seating materials, dual-zone climate control, and a large central display with smartphone connectivity contribute to a well-appointed driving environment. Thoughtful driver-support features help boost confidence on busy roads, while generous trunk space adds versatility for errands or longer trips. With its combination of refined comfort, intelligent design, and everyday usability, this midsize sedan offers a compelling choice for drivers who value efficiency and sophistication.

Discover the exceptional 2020 Chevrolet Malibu LT, a mid-size sedan that combines style, performance, and cutting-edge technology. This vehicle is a true testament to Chevrolet's commitment to delivering exceptional value and an unparalleled driving experience.

Boasting a sleek and modern exterior in a stunning Blue hue, the Malibu LT is sure to turn heads wherever you go. Under the hood, you'll find a powerful 1.5L DOHC engine paired with a smooth-shifting CVT transmission and front-wheel drive, delivering an impressive balance of efficiency and responsiveness. With an EPA-estimated 29 MPG in the city and 36 MPG on the highway, this Malibu LT will help you maximize your fuel savings without compromising on performance.

- License Plate Bracket, Front

Stepping inside, you'll be greeted by a well-appointed interior that prioritizes both comfort and convenience. Enjoy the premium audio system with 6 speakers, SiriusXM Radio, and the intuitive Chevrolet Infotainment 3 system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration. Stay comfortable year-round with the automatic dual-zone climate control, while the heated front seats and power-adjustable driver's seat provide a personalized driving experience.

Safety is a top priority in the Malibu LT, with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance features. Enjoy the peace of mind provided by the rear-view camera, electronic stability control, and a suite of airbags, including dual front, side-impact, and overhead airbags. The OnStar and Chevrolet connected services system also offers emergency communication capabilities, ensuring you're always connected and protected.

Complement the Malibu LT's impressive features with the sleek 17-inch alloy wheels and body-colored bumpers, creating a harmonious blend of style and substance. With the power of Chevrolet's engineering and the attention to detail that sets this sedan apart, the 2020 Malibu LT is a truly exceptional value proposition.

At our dealership, we're committed to providing our customers with a seamless and enjoyable purchasing experience. We invite you to visit our showroom and take this remarkable Malibu LT for a test drive. Experience the difference for yourself and discover why the 2020 Chevrolet Malibu LT should be your next vehicle.
Sanborn Chevrolet has been providing professional service, and quality new and used cars, trucks and SUVs to central California since 1971. From that time, our Lodi Chevrolet dealership has developed a reputation for doing business genuinely and fairly. Come in to see our wide variety of inventory, and you will be greeted with a handshake and a smile by one of our friendly and knowledgeable sales associates.

description:
This 2013 Honda Civic Sdn LX, has a Polished Metal Metallic exterior and an Gray interior color. 76,065 miles. Stock Number 26171T. You can connect with us by calling 508-366-8888. No Accidents! Convenience
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
Powertrain and Mechanical
  • Variable valve timing - Change your output. There are a lot of variables in your drive, so why should your engine always operate the same? With variable valve timing, the engine is efficient at both low and high RPM's, so you get better fuel efficiency, cleaner emissions and improved performance. Variable valve timing provides a better drive, every time.
Safety and Security
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Selective Internet access - a more focused delivery. Selective internet access allows you to tailor the features for your feed, such as sports scores, local news, or current weather. When it comes to getting what you want, selective internet access is a net gain.

Experience the ultimate in power, capability, and luxury with this stunning 2021 Ram 2500 Limited. This one-owner vehicle boasts a clean CARFAX report and a host of premium features that will elevate your driving experience to new heights.

• Clean CARFAX
• One Owner Carfax
• Mega Cab

Under the hood, you'll find the impressive Cummins 6.7L I6 Turbodiesel engine, paired with a 6-speed automatic transmission and 4-wheel drive. This powertrain delivers unparalleled towing and hauling capabilities, making it the perfect companion for your toughest jobs or your next adventure.

• 6.7L I-6 Diesel Turbocharged (Cummins)
• Limited Level 1 Equipment Group
• Auto Level Rear Air Suspension
• Adaptive Steering System
• Painted Front and Rear Bumpers
• 5th Wheel/Gooseneck Towing Prep Group
• Tri-Fold Tonneau Cover
• 17 Speaker harman kardon Premium Sound
• Surround View Camera System
• Adaptive Cruise Control with Stop
• Lane Keep Assist
• Heated and Ventilated Front Seats
• Heated Rear Seats
• Digital Rearview Mirror

Step inside this Ram 2500 Limited, and you'll be surrounded by a level of luxury and technology that is unmatched in the segment. The spacious Mega Cab offers ample room for passengers and cargo, while the premium leather-wrapped interior and advanced infotainment system ensure a truly exceptional driving experience.

The Limited Level 1 Equipment Group elevates this vehicle with features like a 12-inch touchscreen display, a 17-speaker harman kardon premium sound system, and a surround-view camera system. The adaptive steering system and adaptive cruise control with stop-and-go functionality provide enhanced maneuverability and safety, while the tri-fold tonneau cover and 5th wheel/gooseneck towing prep group make this Ram 2500 the ultimate work truck.

Whether you're tackling tough jobs or seeking a comfortable and capable daily driver, this 2021 Ram 2500 Limited is the perfect choice. Experience the power, luxury, and technology that set this vehicle apart from the competition. Schedule a test drive today and discover the true meaning of premium performance.
